407
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,670
Chceli by ste si ma kúpiť?

408
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:45,600
Tadiaľto, pane!

409
00:31:46,770 --> 00:31:48,740
Vyzerá byť silný,

410
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:50,740
